      "asbval:evidence_quote": "We have also incorporated tools for generating previously-described analyses characterizing the correlation and potential cooperativity between two TF binding sites within the same regulatory element",
      "asbval:note": "Paper mentions tools for analyzing cooperativity between TF binding sites but does not specify output format (CSV), column names (annotation_pair, z_score, p_value, variability_excess), or the specific structure described in the claim.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-nmeth-4401",
