      "asbval:note": "SnapATAC is not mentioned anywhere in the provided passages. The paper does not benchmark chromVAR against SnapATAC. chromVAR is compared to PCA and 'other peak-based approaches' but SnapATAC is not named as a comparison target.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-nmeth-4401",
      "asbval:supported_raw": "no",
