      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The MOODS C++ library (Version 1.9.3) was used for identifying peaks containing a motif match... We wrapped the MOODS library into an R package, motifmatchr, which enables fast determination of motif presence or positions within genomic regions. The package is available at www.github.com/GreenleafLab/motifmatchr",
      "asbval:note": "motifmatchr is confirmed as an R package for motif matching to peaks.",
      "asbval:perspicacite_kb": "asb-paper-10-1038-nmeth-4401",
