      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "chromVAR first computes a 'raw accessibility deviation'... To account for these technical confounders... The raw accessibility deviations for these background peak sets are used to compute a bias corrected deviation and z-score for each annotation and cell",
