      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The MOODS C++ library (Version 1.9.3) was used for identifying peaks containing a motif match, using a p-value cutoff of 5\u00d710\u22125. As background frequencies we used the nucleotide frequencies across all peaks. We wrapped the MOODS library into an R package, motifmatchr, which enables fast determination of motif presence or positions within genomic regions.",
      "asbval:note": "motifmatchr is confirmed as an R package wrapping MOODS for motif matching in peaks.",
